    "formatted for the Amiga, such as a CG Fonts disk from Gold Disk.\n"
    "The second is an MS-DOS FAIS disk not yet formatted for the Amiga,\n"
    "such as a TypeDirector font disk from Agfa Compugraphic.  Using an\n"
    "MS-DOS disk directly requires an MS-DOS handler, such as CrossDOS.\n"
    "\n"
    "The little file folder button invokes the standard file requester\n"
    "for directory selection.  Only directories are displayed, and only\n"
