    "a marked entry to remove the mark.\n"
    "\n"
    "Intellifont typeface names on the\n"
    "Amiga are those specified by the\n"
    "typeface vendor, with spaces\n"
    "removed.  They cannot be changed.\n"
    "\n"
    "Press Esc to exit Help.  Select to\n"
    "continue.",

    "Install Marked Typefaces\n"
    "\n"
    "Selecting this button initiates the installation of all the marked\n"
    "Source Typefaces into the Destination Font Drawer.  Included in\n"
    "this installation process is a list of standard sizes to be used by\n"
    "applications when presenting their font selection menus.  These\n"
    "sizes are taken from the environment text file ENV:sys/Intellifont,\n"
    "if it exists.  You must exit Intellifont to change this file.\n"
    "\n"
    "Technical Note: Installation creates three files for each typeface\n"
    "installed:  <name>.font, <name>.otag, and\n"
