    "element of the Fonts: assign path.  The Fonts: Path Component\n"
    "button makes it easy to select such directories.\n"
    "\n"
    "Other directories are allowed.  Typefaces installed there would not\n"
    "be accessable by most applications.  Using a non-Fonts: directory\n"
    "is appropriate if Intellifont is being used to generate Amiga\n"
