    "library) for this information.  For outline typefaces, the\n"
    "sizes available are arbitrary.  This window provides a way\n"
    "to specify which sizes to tell applications about.\n"
    "\n"
    "Also, for often-used sizes, an Amiga bitmap form of the\n"
    "font can be created.  This takes more disk space, but is\n"
